      "instruction": "<p>Top, tail and grate your <strong>carrot[s]</strong></p><p>Cut your <strong>cucumber[s]</strong> in half lengthways, then slice finely at an angle</p><p>Slice your <strong>red chilli[es]</strong> finely</p><p>Strip your <strong>mint leaves</strong> from their stems and chop finely, discard the stems</p>",
