    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>rice vinegar</strong> and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> in a bowl with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>grated carrot</strong>, <strong>sliced cucumber</strong>, <strong>chopped mint</strong> and most of the <strong>sliced chilli</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) – this is your <strong>quick-pickled salad</strong></p><p>Reserve the <strong>remaining sliced chilli</strong> for garnish</p>",
