    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>cornflour</strong> and 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>flour</strong> in a bowl with your <strong>ground</strong> <strong>turmeric</strong>, 60ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [90ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[120ml]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Whisk until a smooth, thick batter remains – this is your <strong>turmeric batter</strong></p>",
