    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>hake strips</strong> to the <strong>turmeric batter</strong> and give everything a good mix up until well coated – these are your <strong>coated hake strips</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1663090903888-x200.jpg",
