          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>mayo</strong> and <strong>tamarind paste</strong> in a small bowl – this is your <strong>tamarind mayo</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>tortillas</strong> to a plate and pop them in the <strong>microwave</strong> for 1-2 min or until warmed through</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
